snippet.title: Sea of Thieves Season 14: Official Content Update Video
snippet.description:
Sea of Thieves Season 14 is all about making mischief. From priming traps with fireworks to sneaking around as a treasure chest, learn all about the new tools, toys and techniques that await in this fresh Content Update video!

----------------------------------------

Buy the game and forge your own legend: https://www.seaofthieves.com/buy
